sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant IMP as importlib
    participant BI as deepview.plugins.builtin
    participant DEC as "@register_plugin"
    participant G as _REGISTERED_PLUGINS (module global)
    participant CTX as AnalysisContext
    participant PR as PluginRegistry

    Note over IMP,BI: Tier 1 (import-time side effect)
    IMP->>BI: import deepview.plugins.builtin
    BI->>DEC: class definitions apply decorator
    DEC->>G: _REGISTERED_PLUGINS[name] = cls

    Note over CTX,PR: First access to context.plugins
    CTX->>PR: PluginRegistry(self) via @property
    PR->>PR: discover() - once

    PR->>BI: import deepview.plugins.builtin
    PR->>G: get_registered_plugins()
    G-->>PR: {name: cls, ...}

    Note over PR: Tier 2 - entry points
    PR->>PR: importlib.metadata.entry_points(group="deepview.plugins")
    loop each entry point
        PR->>PR: ep.load() -> cls
        alt name already present
            PR->>PR: log.warning("duplicate_plugin_name") - skip
        else new
            PR->>PR: _plugins[name] = cls
        end
    end

    Note over PR: Tier 3 - directory scan
    PR->>PR: for path in config.plugin_paths + config_dir/plugins
    alt symlink
        PR->>PR: refuse, continue
    else real dir
        PR->>PR: load every *.py (skip underscore prefixed)
    end

    PR-->>CTX: ready
